languages.text: "О! Ты умудрил{mf|ся|ась} явиться сюда и вмешаться в замысел пророчицы, даже не зная, кто она? Но теперь уже поздно. Тебе не прозреть. Остается лишь принять свою участь".

languages.text: "Oh! So you've managed to barge in here and interfere with the Prophetess's designs without even knowing who she is? But it is too late now. You will never attain sight. All you can do is accept your fate."

languages.text: “噢！你甚至都不清楚那位女先知的计划，就在这里狺狺狂吠，横加阻挠？不过，一切都已经太迟了。你永远都无法得到光明。你唯一能做的事情，就是接受你的命运。”
languages.original_text: "Oh! So you've managed to barge in here and interfere with the Prophetess's designs without even knowing who she is? But it is too late now. You will never attain sight. All you can do is accept your fate."

traits.locale_text: “噢！你甚至都不知道那位女先知是谁，就在想方设法侮辱她？但现在已经太迟了。你永远都无法得到光明。你唯一能做的事情，就是接受你的命运。”

languages.text: "Oh! Dann seid Ihr also hierher gelangt und habt die Prophetin beleidigt, ohne zu wissen, wer sie ist? Doch nun ist es zu spät. Ihr werdet niemals Weitsicht erlangen. Euch bleibt nur, Euer Schicksal zu akzeptieren."
languages.original_text: "Oh! So you've managed to barge in here and interfere with the Prophetess's designs without even knowing who she is? But it is too late now. You will never attain sight. All you can do is accept your fate."

languages.text: « Oh ! Or donc, vous avez l'audace de débarquer ici et de compromettre les desseins de la prophétesse sans même savoir qui elle est ? Mais il est trop tard désormais. Vous n'éveillerez jamais votre conscience. Tout ce qui reste à faire, c'est d'accepter votre destin. »
languages.original_text: "Oh! So you've managed to barge in here and interfere with the Prophetess's designs without even knowing who she is? But it is too late now. You will never attain sight. All you can do is accept your fate."

traits.locale_text: « Oh ! Vous insultez donc la prophétesse sans même savoir qui elle est ? Mais il est trop tard désormais. Vous n'éveillerez jamais votre conscience. Tout ce qui reste à faire, c'est d'accepter votre destin. »

languages.text: 「ほう！では彼女が何者かも知らずに無理やりここに押し入り、預言者の計画を邪魔したというわけか？だが、もう遅い。お前達にもう『見る』ことはできない。己の運命を受け入れるしかないのだ」
languages.original_text: "Oh! So you've managed to barge in here and interfere with the Prophetess's designs without even knowing who she is? But it is too late now. You will never attain sight. All you can do is accept your fate."
